                        "content": "The nurse is caring for a client with prostate cancer who is being treated with a hormone therapy. What would the nurse monitor for in order to evaluate the effect of this treatment?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "a0f7d178f7b728b8bba7ef20ddeca62d",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Evaluating 评价",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nHormone therapy (androgen deprivation) is a mode of treatment for prostatic cancer. The goal is to limit the amount of circulating androgens because prostate cells depend on androgen for cellular maintenance. Deprivation of androgen often can lead to regression of disease and improvement of symptoms. The remaining options do not identify the goals of this form of treatment.",
                        "id": "1c2bd158b69749b7aa731753426df163",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "c927870cd2c34584852c161761e42a61",
                                "content": "Avoid driving the car for a few days."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "d0c80632be0d4770aefdd6a36caa9c7b",
                                "content": "Restrict fluid intake to prevent incontinence."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "993434d2c3284ea98a1f65199d808ddb",
                                "content": "Avoid lifting objects heavier than 20 lb (9 kg) for at least 6 weeks."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "3a84a3db08b8442a97bbe8d263c89ea4",
                                "content": "Notify the primary health care provider if small blood clots are noticed during urination."
                            }
